    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/34cb7748d9c7e2df664fa945130b23f7.avif?t=1746633690\" width=612 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《尘世之仪》的核心元素在于快节奏、动作感十足的近战战斗系统，玩家将在激烈对决中猛击按键，击败敌人并赢取丰厚奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以选择不同角色，每个角色拥有独特的背景故事、战斗风格和技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充分运用多样的技能组合与战术搭配，收集并制作物品，击败敌人，阻止国王的入侵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以在游戏一开始时就选择单人模式或最多 5 人的多人合作模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在庇护所中还可以和好友进行切磋，赢取额外奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >需要注意的是，队伍人数越多，敌人会越多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗与升级</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找散布在各处的技能点和物品，解锁全新的战斗策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您不仅可以与其他玩家交换物品，还可以在庇护所使用技能点，定制个性化的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个区域都有一名门卫守护，击败门卫后，玩家可以随时重返该区域进行更多挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重新进入区域时，玩家将在更新的地图中面对全新的敌人组合，收集新的物品。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特的角色和技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/9e10e75e533b4db3b596ef496a245ddb.poster.avif?t=1746633690\" width=612 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/9e10e75e533b4db3b596ef496a245ddb.webm?t=1746633690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/9e10e75e533b4db3b596ef496a245ddb.mp4?t=1746633690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在姿态系统中，每个角色自带两种游戏风格，玩家可以通过技能交换、升级和物品实现个性化定制。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多人合作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/37c81a948805ba6dfefded3d461c299f.poster.avif?t=1746633690\" width=612 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/37c81a948805ba6dfefded3d461c299f.webm?t=1746633690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/37c81a948805ba6dfefded3d461c299f.mp4?t=1746633690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可在游戏开始时选择多人模式，与好友一起共享合作战斗的乐趣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在多人合作模式中，玩家将面临不同的敌人和地形。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/7e5a17d81a765a66f774d8b19aa621bd.poster.avif?t=1746633690\" width=612 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/7e5a17d81a765a66f774d8b19aa621bd.webm?t=1746633690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/7e5a17d81a765a66f774d8b19aa621bd.mp4?t=1746633690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快节奏、反应迅速的近战战斗，重点强调通过破坏敌人的架势来打断攻击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色拥有轻击、重击和蓄力攻击，玩家可以无缝组合不同的攻击方式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用独特的疾跑、躲避和空中攻击，根据不同敌人调整策略。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合各角色的招架、弹反和格挡特性，实现反攻。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>敌人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/8b9d6acaddaae98e4f44cfbda84d3b7c.poster.avif?t=1746633690\" width=612 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/8b9d6acaddaae98e4f44cfbda84d3b7c.webm?t=1746633690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1655990/extras/8b9d6acaddaae98e4f44cfbda84d3b7c.mp4?t=1746633690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将遭遇各类攻势强劲的敌人，每个敌人都拥有独特的战斗风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 各种派系也会影响战斗。如果派系之间存在敌对关系，玩家可以利用这一点，迫使敌人互相厮杀！</p></li></ul>",
